### 产品分类管理API测试
### 接口版本：v1
### 基础URL：http://localhost:8080/api/v1/product/categories

### 1. 创建产品分类
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/product/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "智能家居",
    "code": "smart_home",
    "parentId": null,
    "level": 1,
    "sortOrder": 0,
    "icon": "icon-home",
    "description": "智能家居设备分类",
    "type": "CUSTOM",
    "status": "ACTIVE",
    "tenantId": 1
}

### 2. 创建子分类
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/product/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "智能照明",
    "code": "smart_lighting",
    "parentId": 1,
    "level": 2,
    "sortOrder": 0,
    "icon": "icon-lightbulb",
    "description": "智能照明设备分类",
    "type": "CUSTOM",
    "status": "ACTIVE",
    "tenantId": 1
}

### 3. 创建另一个根分类
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/product/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "工业设备",
    "code": "industrial_devices",
    "parentId": null,
    "level": 1,
    "sortOrder": 1,
    "icon": "icon-industry",
    "description": "工业设备分类",
    "type": "CUSTOM",
    "status": "ACTIVE",
    "tenantId": 1
}

### 4. 获取产品分类详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/product/categories/1

### 5. 分页查询产品分类
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/product/categories?pageNo=1&pageSize=10

### 6. 根据父分类查询
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/product/categories?parentId=1&pageNo=1&pageSize=10

### 7. 按名称模糊查询
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/product/categories?name=智能&pageNo=1&pageSize=10

### 8. 查询分类树
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/product/categories/tree?tenantId=1

### 9. 查询子分类
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/product/categories/children?parentId=1&tenantId=1

### 10. 检查分类标识符是否存在
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/product/categories/check-code?code=smart_home&tenantId=1

### 11. 更新产品分类
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/product/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "智能家居设备",
    "description": "更新后的智能家居设备分类描述",
    "icon": "icon-home-updated",
    "sortOrder": 1
}

### 12. 批量删除产品分类
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/product/categories/batch
Content-Type: application/json

[2, 3]

### 13. 删除产品分类
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/product/categories/1

